1
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:35,940
[Light to the Night]

2
00:01:39,540 --> 00:01:40,580
[Yunshan Zizhu Restaurant]

3
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:41,930
It's cold outside.

4
00:01:42,350 --> 00:01:43,490
How about I drive you?

5
00:01:44,150 --> 00:01:44,690
No need.

6
00:01:44,710 --> 00:01:45,740
My company is close by.

7
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,540
It's just a short walk.

8
00:01:47,430 --> 00:01:48,100
Go on, get back to work.

9
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:52,370
You...

10
00:01:57,900 --> 00:02:00,900
[Light to the Night]
[Episode 28]

11
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:06,330
So, since that time,

12
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,940
you had been planning to kill Captain Ran?

13
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,890
Quite the opposite.

14
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,010
When I discovered

15
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:19,450
that he was a cop,

16
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,570
I actually stopped worrying.

17
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:24,170
At the time, I thought

18
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,100
Qiao Suqing

19
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,540
must have been acting.

20
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:29,730
She wanted to use the cop

21
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:31,100
as a cover for herself.

22
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:34,100
She was carrying too many secrets.

23
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:37,010
How could she possibly

24
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:37,820
be with a cop?

25
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,340
But over the following months,

26
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:44,170
Qiao Suqing clearly became cold toward me.

27
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,490
I'd send her messages,

28
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:48,010
but she rarely replied.

29
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:50,580
When she answered the phone, she'd say she was working.

30
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,540
She always said she was busy.

31
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,010
She changed.

32
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,940
I couldn't help myself,

33
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:00,610
so I went back to Weiyang.

34
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:03,100
I wanted to give her a surprise.

35
00:03:04,470 --> 00:03:06,380
I wanted to spend the Chinese New Year with her.

36
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:06,890
Hello.

37
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:08,290
Please wrap these two up for me.

38
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,060
Do you want to wear it now?

39
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,130
I can take the tags off for you.

40
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:13,260
Sure.

41
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:14,060
Thanks.

42
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:25,610
Welcome.

43
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:50,100
I can never forget

44
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,850
the look in her eyes back then.

45
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,220
I had never seen her

46
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,730
smile so happily.

47
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:02,570
I thought about it for two whole days.

48
00:04:05,190 --> 00:04:06,130
In the end, I decided

49
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:07,220
I had to go talk to her.

50
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:10,610
She's in great danger now.

51
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:12,450
I must protect her.

52
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:16,900
But then, right at that moment,

53
00:04:19,830 --> 00:04:20,730
I received a call

54
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:21,930
from her.

55
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:26,540
You're going to turn yourself in?

56
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,170
I've confessed everything to the police.

57
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,610
I'm the one who killed everyone.

58
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:35,980
Including you.

59
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:39,930
When do you plan to turn yourself in?

60
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,850
Tomorrow morning.

61
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,140
Why didn't

62
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,490
the cop just arrest you?

63
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:53,340
He promised me

64
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:58,460
that I could finish this Chinese New Year's Eve.

65
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,460
I'll come find you right now.

66
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:05,930
I'll stay with you.

67
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:07,730
Meng,

68
00:05:09,310 --> 00:05:10,100
don't come.

69
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:12,780
I already promised

70
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,730
that cop

71
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:14,930
that I wouldn't run.

72
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,050
He also promised me

73
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:19,850
that tonight,

74
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:23,050
he would spend the Chinese New Year with me.

75
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,340
I had made an appointment with him.

76
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,020
When I finish my part-time job tonight,

77
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:31,900
he'll come to pick me up.

78
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,660
Tomorrow morning,

79
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,340
he'll go with me to turn myself in.

80
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:40,560
Meng,

81
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,610
you must live a good life.

82
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,410
Sister,

83
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,730
wait for me.

84
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,930
I'm taking the train tomorrow morning

85
00:05:50,950 --> 00:05:51,460
back to Weiyang.

86
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,850
I'll go with you to turn yourself in.

87
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:54,850
No.

88
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:56,730
Absolutely not.

89
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,220
You finally have

90
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,540
a home of your own.

91
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,410
Just

92
00:06:01,390 --> 00:06:03,460
stay there and live well.

93
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,850
Live the life you want.

94
00:07:00,870 --> 00:07:01,410
Previously,

95
00:07:01,430 --> 00:07:03,170
when I was tailing Qiao Suqing,

96
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,540
I visited the place where she worked part-time.

97
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:09,930
I noticed a section of the road

98
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:11,410
with a construction site in the middle.

99
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,460
So I thought of using my old method,

100
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,850
which was staging an accident.

101
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,780
To ensure success,

102
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,490
I went back to the mall.

103
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,410
I bought a wig,

104
00:07:28,750 --> 00:07:30,700
and I even bought the same

105
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,460
Bowls coat and red scarf as Qiao Suqing.

106
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,290
I dressed up just like her.

107
00:07:36,430 --> 00:07:37,020
First,

108
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:39,020
it helped me better attract

109
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,340
the attention of that cop.

110
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:42,050
Second,

111
00:07:43,430 --> 00:07:44,660
if the plan failed,

112
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:47,980
I could still pin the blame on her.

113
00:07:49,310 --> 00:07:50,410
You kept insisting

114
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,460
that you wanted to protect Qiao Suqing.

115
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:53,170
Why would you try to frame her?

116
00:07:53,190 --> 00:07:54,220
Why do you think!

117
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,020
It was for our safety.

118
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,410
I killed Yao,

119
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,370
I killed Xu Zhihong,

120
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:03,780
and I killed Wu Shanlong.

121
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:07,410
But what about her?

122
00:08:10,030 --> 00:08:11,140
She knew clearly that the cop

123
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,500
was investigating us,

124
00:08:14,230 --> 00:08:15,420
yet she still stayed with him.

125
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,140
She lied to me.

126
00:08:18,630 --> 00:08:19,730
She betrayed me.

127
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:21,170
She deserves it.

128
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:22,730
She deserves it!

129
00:08:50,380 --> 00:08:51,740
[Mentor]

130
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,650
Qiao.

131
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,580
Qiao, no!

132
00:10:00,180 --> 00:10:02,580
[Mentor]

133
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:53,900
Xu...

134
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:23,220
I should have killed Ran long ago.

135
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:25,850
If not for him,

136
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,980
Qiao Suqing would never have betrayed me.

137
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,340
She would still be my elder sister,

138
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,610
and I would still be her younger sister.

139
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,180
We could have

140
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,820
lived happily

141
00:11:38,550 --> 00:11:40,250
at home together.

142
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:42,460
Xu Meng, you're not human!

143
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:42,890
Calm down.

144
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,460
Do you have any humanity at all?

145
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:44,820
Xiaohe.

146
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,700
You're the one who killed Uncle Ran!

147
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,100
You're a monster.

148
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,100
A monster!

149
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:50,730
Xu Meng,

150
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:51,890
you have lost your mind

151
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:53,010
and all humanity.

152
00:11:53,030 --> 00:11:54,010
For your own selfish desires,

153
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:55,730
you've openly committed numerous atrocities.

154
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:56,890
Your methods were cruel,

155
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:57,730
and your crimes heinous.

156
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,300
You've harmed so many people

157
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,060
and so many families.

158
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,580
You didn't even spare

159
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,040
the innocent Captain Ran or the child.

160
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,650
This is unconscionable.

161
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:05,590
You are pure evil!

162
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:32,850
Where is it?

163
00:12:53,630 --> 00:12:54,300
No reason

164
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:56,220
is an excuse to break the law.

165
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:57,890
No crime

166
00:12:57,910 --> 00:12:59,220
is ever truly foolproof.

167
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,130
Crime always leaves a trace.

168
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,530
No one escapes

169
00:13:03,910 --> 00:13:05,220
the long arm of the law.

170
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,250
Anyone who commits a crime

171
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:09,530
will be exposed to the law,

172
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,530
exposed to justice,

173
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,460
and exposed

174
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,820
to the light of day.

175
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:26,460
[New York Block]

176
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:45,180
Xiaohe.

177
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,180
I'm sorry.

178
00:13:50,550 --> 00:13:51,100
Please also

179
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,820
tell Uncle He that I'm sorry.

180
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:56,060
Everything was my fault.

181
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:58,530
I brought this on myself.

182
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,580
It's only natural

183
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,180
that you hate me.

184
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:05,180
Qiao Suqing,

185
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:07,730
I won't hate you.

186
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:10,010
The law will judge

187
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:11,220
everything you've done.

188
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:13,940
I will completely forget

189
00:14:14,750 --> 00:14:15,820
the Qiao Suqing standing before me.

190
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:19,610
I will only remember

191
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:21,420
that summer of 1997,

192
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,650
and the Ms. Qiao who took care of me

193
00:14:24,670 --> 00:14:25,580
all day and all night.

194
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,220
Thank you.

195
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,770
When their legal rights are violated,

196
00:15:09,390 --> 00:15:10,130
the law

197
00:15:10,150 --> 00:15:11,770
is the only weapon to protect oneself.

198
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:14,060
But in the June 30th case,

199
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:15,980
the criminal suspect

200
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,220
represented by Xu Meng

201
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:18,770
did not choose the law

202
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:21,340
after being harmed.

203
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:23,340
Instead, she vented her anger

204
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,250
through personal revenge.

205
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:26,130
One wrong step led to another,

206
00:15:26,550 --> 00:15:27,490
and things escalated.

207
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:30,340
They kept crossing legal red lines

208
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,130
and challenging human decency,

209
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,700
becoming perpetrators through and through.

210
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:36,650
On the path of crime,

211
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:37,680
they went further and further,

212
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,490
eventually sliding

213
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:41,250
into the abyss of no return.

214
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:44,060
They have to face the judgment of law and justice.

215
00:15:45,540 --> 00:15:49,340
[February 1, 2003]

216
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:41,980
I didn't know Officer Ran,

217
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:44,610
but you said he was a good man.

218
00:16:45,670 --> 00:16:47,060
How could such a good person

219
00:16:48,030 --> 00:16:49,130
just be gone?

220
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,940
Did you just get off the train?

221
00:16:59,630 --> 00:17:00,180
Yeah.

222
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:01,530
Why?

223
00:17:08,350 --> 00:17:09,460
I'm going to wash my hands.

224
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:36,700
[Kunhai→Weiyang, February 1, 2003]

225
00:17:55,830 --> 00:17:56,490
Sister,

226
00:17:58,030 --> 00:17:59,490
do you still want to surrender?

227
00:18:06,270 --> 00:18:07,420
If you still want to go,

228
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:09,140
I'll go with you.

229
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:13,940
I know it might be

230
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:15,090
the wrong time to say this,

231
00:18:15,790 --> 00:18:16,860
but I still want to say it.

232
00:18:18,070 --> 00:18:19,140
Officer Ran's death

233
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:20,940
might have been fate.

234
00:18:21,550 --> 00:18:22,330
It's God giving you

235
00:18:22,350 --> 00:18:23,730
a chance to choose again.

236
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:33,770
From now on,

237
00:18:35,510 --> 00:18:36,490
no matter what I face,

238
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,380
I will choose

239
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:44,700
to be a good person.

240
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:50,810
Sister,

241
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,700
come home with me.

242
00:18:53,830 --> 00:18:55,090
It's only safe if you leave here.

243
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,490
The home I wanted

244
00:19:04,350 --> 00:19:05,420
is already gone.

245
00:19:06,310 --> 00:19:07,940
The home you want doesn't matter.

246
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,040
Safety is what matters.

247
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:15,810
Meng,

248
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:19,140
you should go.

249
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:26,700
Aren't you afraid that staying

250
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,730
in Weiyang is dangerous?

251
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:34,860
I just want to stay in the sunlight.

252
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:43,730
Even if it's dangerous sunlight.

253
00:21:14,620 --> 00:21:16,860
[Six months later, Weiyang People's Procuratorate filed a public prosecution]

254
00:21:16,860 --> 00:21:19,260
[Defendant Xu Meng is suspected of arson, intentional homicide,]

255
00:21:19,260 --> 00:21:21,360
[and false accusation; sentencing recommendation: death penalty]

256
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:23,760
[Defendant Qiao Suqing is suspected of intentional homicide, harboring,]

257
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:26,060
[and false accusation; sentencing recommendation: life imprisonment]

258
00:21:38,740 --> 00:21:43,740
[Kiddo]

259
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:45,620
It's about time.

260
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:47,730
Why is there no news?

261
00:21:51,660 --> 00:21:52,740
[WeChat: 1 contact sent a message]

262
00:21:58,920 --> 00:21:59,630
The sentencing just finished.

263
00:22:00,350 --> 00:22:01,220
Xu got the death penalty.

264
00:22:01,830 --> 00:22:02,620
Qiao got life.

265
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:17,940
[Jiajia Cola]

266
00:22:28,310 --> 00:22:28,980
Hey, Meng.

267
00:22:29,750 --> 00:22:30,570
Hurry up and get up.

268
00:22:31,110 --> 00:22:32,290
Let's go for a walk downstairs.

269
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:33,570
No.

270
00:22:33,590 --> 00:22:34,490
I'm going

271
00:22:34,510 --> 00:22:35,860
to practice "turtle breathing".

272
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,050
"Turtle breathing," my foot.

273
00:22:37,070 --> 00:22:38,220
If you don't move around,

274
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:39,420
you'll be breathing your last soon!

275
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:39,980
I'm not going.

276
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:41,570
I'm about to fall asleep.

277
00:22:41,590 --> 00:22:42,810
Take a walk downstairs.

278
00:22:42,990 --> 00:22:44,530
No, I'm not going.

279
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:45,050
Let's go.

280
00:22:45,070 --> 00:22:45,940
No.

281
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:46,810
I said I'm not going.

282
00:22:46,830 --> 00:22:47,380
Come on.

283
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:48,290
Help!

284
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:49,330
Is anyone there?

285
00:22:49,350 --> 00:22:51,250
Manager!

286
00:22:51,270 --> 00:22:53,050
Come and change my room.

287
00:22:53,070 --> 00:22:54,290
I can't stay in the same room

288
00:22:54,310 --> 00:22:55,810
as this nutcase anymore!

289
00:22:55,830 --> 00:22:56,420
Shut up.

290
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:57,460
Manager,

291
00:22:57,480 --> 00:22:58,460
where are you?

292
00:22:58,480 --> 00:22:59,620
Help. Somebody!

293
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,750
Shut up.

