591
00:36:29,190 --> 00:36:29,980
don't forget about us.

592
00:36:30,510 --> 00:36:31,650
Where are you looking?

593
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:33,650
He's right here.

594
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:37,780
Don't forget about us.

595
00:36:40,630 --> 00:36:41,340
How could I?

596
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:43,610
Every one of you

597
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:45,010
is in my heart.

598
00:36:47,510 --> 00:36:48,050
Dad!

599
00:36:52,300 --> 00:36:52,980
Xiaohe,

600
00:36:53,230 --> 00:36:54,390
Uncle Ran is leaving.

601
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:55,820
Hurry up and say goodbye.

602
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,010
Goodbye,

603
00:37:00,710 --> 00:37:01,170
Uncle Ran.

604
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:03,900
See? We're all doing quite well.

605
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:05,460
You can head back to Beijing in peace.

606
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:08,430
Don't worry.

607
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:09,780
I'm at ease now.

608
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:11,860
Xiaohe,

609
00:37:12,710 --> 00:37:13,980
that uniform really suits you.

610
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,300
Keep it up.

611
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:17,260
You'll be better than me.

612
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:23,490
The Beijing-bound

613
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:25,130
Train Z118

614
00:37:25,150 --> 00:37:26,380
is about to depart.

615
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:28,260
Passengers, please board the train now.

616
00:37:30,440 --> 00:37:31,050
Sir,

617
00:37:31,590 --> 00:37:32,210
I should go.

618
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:37,340
Ran,

619
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:38,530
go on then.

620
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,010
But we have a deal.

621
00:37:40,630 --> 00:37:41,650
You cannot

622
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:42,490
leave and never return.

623
00:37:43,150 --> 00:37:43,740
From time to time,

624
00:37:43,760 --> 00:37:44,780
you must come home and visit.

625
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:46,130
Otherwise,

626
00:37:46,150 --> 00:37:47,530
we will be worried about you.

627
00:37:47,840 --> 00:37:48,420
Understand?

628
00:37:50,510 --> 00:37:50,880
Okay.

629
00:37:58,360 --> 00:37:59,420
Say something.

630
00:38:00,030 --> 00:38:00,900
Say...

631
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:01,260
Right.

632
00:38:01,670 --> 00:38:03,380
We miss you all the time.

633
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:04,460
We're always thinking about you.

634
00:38:05,670 --> 00:38:06,010
Captain Ran,

635
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:07,860
I'm Zheng Zhong.

636
00:38:08,400 --> 00:38:09,340
Even though you've never met me,

637
00:38:09,710 --> 00:38:10,530
I can recite

638
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:11,300
all of your books from memory.

639
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:12,940
The theories in those books,

640
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:14,090
to this very day,

641
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:15,570
we are still using them.

642
00:38:20,670 --> 00:38:21,260
You hear it?

643
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:22,490
I hear you.

644
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:24,610
I hear all of you.

645
00:38:27,030 --> 00:38:28,420
Thank you for still keeping me in your thoughts.

646
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:30,130
And I wish you

647
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:31,310
success in your work

648
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:34,090
and good health.

649
00:38:36,720 --> 00:38:37,350
I'm going now.

650
00:38:47,800 --> 00:38:48,210
Sir,

651
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:51,010
I'm leaving.

652
00:40:12,230 --> 00:40:14,490
Ran Fangxu has truly left this time!

653
00:40:15,070 --> 00:40:16,740
Take care of yourselves.

654
00:40:37,590 --> 00:40:39,300
I really do miss Captain Ran.

655
00:40:44,230 --> 00:40:45,130
I always have.

656
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,130
Don't worry,

657
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:49,650
Uncle Ran.

658
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:52,740
I will carry it on.

659
00:40:55,110 --> 00:40:55,570
We'll carry it all on.

660
00:40:57,920 --> 00:41:00,090
Goodbye!

661
00:42:22,020 --> 00:42:30,540
[Light to the Night - The End]

662
00:42:32,780 --> 00:42:37,500
♪I hear a voice from the depths of the valley♪

663
00:42:38,500 --> 00:42:41,860
♪Tinged with madness♪

664
00:42:42,380 --> 00:42:45,700
♪And hysteria♪

665
00:42:47,620 --> 00:42:52,340
♪I see the familiar self in my dream♪

666
00:42:53,940 --> 00:42:57,300
♪So avoidant♪

667
00:42:57,820 --> 00:43:01,140
♪So distraught♪

668
00:43:02,780 --> 00:43:07,500
♪That was a faraway memory♪

669
00:43:09,100 --> 00:43:12,460
♪I'm praying♪

670
00:43:12,940 --> 00:43:16,300
♪For my fate♪

671
00:43:18,580 --> 00:43:23,220
♪That's a secret that only belongs to time♪

672
00:43:24,460 --> 00:43:27,820
♪It's only a secret♪

673
00:43:28,300 --> 00:43:31,660
♪If no one brings it up♪

674
00:43:32,900 --> 00:43:36,420
♪Who will complete the puzzle of this lie♪

675
00:43:36,860 --> 00:43:40,580
♪Line by line, whose name are they calling out?♪

676
00:43:40,700 --> 00:43:44,380
♪Nightfall is the finale of all answers♪

677
00:43:44,380 --> 00:43:48,060
♪Only belonging to this barren land♪

678
00:43:48,140 --> 00:43:52,020
♪Who came from the forsaken crowd?♪

679
00:43:52,180 --> 00:43:56,060
♪Caressing a rusted body♪

680
00:43:56,060 --> 00:43:59,900
♪Stashing the secret on a certain floor♪

681
00:43:59,900 --> 00:44:07,740
♪Without making any ripples♪

682
00:44:10,580 --> 00:44:16,220
♪Any ripples♪

683
00:44:16,700 --> 00:44:20,220
♪Who will complete the puzzle of this lie♪

684
00:44:20,700 --> 00:44:24,380
♪Line by line, whose name are they calling out?♪

685
00:44:24,460 --> 00:44:28,140
♪Nightfall is the finale of all answers♪

686
00:44:28,140 --> 00:44:31,860
♪Only belonging to this barren land♪

687
00:44:31,900 --> 00:44:35,820
♪Who came from the forsaken crowd?♪

688
00:44:35,980 --> 00:44:39,860
♪Caressing a rusted body♪

689
00:44:39,860 --> 00:44:43,700
♪Stashing the secret on a certain floor♪

690
00:44:43,700 --> 00:44:54,340
♪In the loneliness of nightfall♪
